snippet.title: Rise of The Fianna World Exclusive Reveal Trailer – The PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Rise of the Fianna is a tactical RPG set in a Celtic fantasy world of myth and legend. Control a party of bards, druids and warriors as you explore the world and seek to unravel its mysteries.
